{"acceptance_criteria":"","actor":"","agent_state":"","assignee":null,"await_id":"","await_type":"","close_reason":"根因：MD_ENTER_SPAN/MD_LEAVE_SPAN 宏直接调用 enter_span/leave_span 回调不检查 NULL。我们传了 null 回调，当 markdown 包含 inline code（双反引号）时 md4c 调用 NULL 函数指针 → SIGSEGV。修复：提供 no-op span 回调。","closed_at":"2026-03-03T16:13:01Z","closed_by_session":"","compacted_at":null,"compacted_at_commit":null,"compaction_level":0,"content_hash":"0ae34f38257738b119536f89a70bd621e6625fa32091c016841044b2595d7186","created_at":"2026-03-03T15:57:49Z","created_by":"lee","crystallizes":0,"defer_until":null,"description":"md4c 解析 hover markdown 时 SIGSEGV 导致 yacd 整个进程崩溃。coredumpctl 显示大量 SIGABRT（wasmtime 信号处理器将 SIGSEGV 转为 SIGABRT）。崩溃栈: md_parse → md_process_doc → md_process_all_blocks → md_process_leaf_block → md_process_normal_block_contents。vendored md4c.c 与 upstream master 完全一致（最新版），已知 CVE 应已修复。已添加 debug 日志记录 markdown 内容，等下次崩溃复现后分析触发内容。可能方向：1) 用特定 markdown 输入复现 2) 考虑在子进程中运行 md4c 隔离崩溃 3) 向 md4c upstream 报 bug","design":"","due_at":null,"ephemeral":0,"estimated_minutes":null,"event_kind":"","external_ref":null,"hook_bead":"","id":"yac-2rb","is_template":0,"issue_type":"bug","last_activity":null,"metadata":"{}","mol_type":"","notes":"","original_size":null,"owner":"loyalpartner@163.com","payload":"","pinned":0,"priority":1,"quality_score":null,"rig":"","role_bead":"","role_type":"","sender":"","source_repo":"","source_system":"","spec_id":"","status":"closed","target":"","timeout_ns":0,"title":"Bug: md4c segfault in md_process_normal_block_contents crashes yacd","updated_at":"2026-03-03T16:13:01Z","waiters":"","wisp_type":"","work_type":""}
