{"acceptance_criteria":"","actor":"","agent_state":"","assignee":null,"await_id":"","await_type":"","close_reason":"修复：移除 yac#daemon_stop() 中的 socket 文件删除逻辑，只保留 channel 关闭。daemon 自己管理 socket 生命周期（退出时自动清理）。","closed_at":"2026-03-03T15:47:02Z","closed_by_session":"","compacted_at":null,"compacted_at_commit":null,"compaction_level":0,"content_hash":"153ddf5e17a910f834068f28b6233efedfbdb41fccdafd100bcffc13e0c05d62","created_at":"2026-03-03T15:42:14Z","created_by":"lee","crystallizes":0,"defer_until":null,"description":"复现步骤：打开 vim → 使用 picker 打开文件 → 退出 vim → 再次打开 vim 打开 picker → 此时会有两个 yacd 进程存在。说明退出 Vim 时 yacd daemon 没有正确退出，导致下次启动时又创建了一个新进程。需要排查 Vim 退出时的 daemon 生命周期管理。","design":"","due_at":null,"ephemeral":0,"estimated_minutes":null,"event_kind":"","external_ref":null,"hook_bead":"","id":"yac-n0r","is_template":0,"issue_type":"bug","last_activity":null,"metadata":"{}","mol_type":"","notes":"根因：yac#daemon_stop() 在 VimLeave 时删除 socket 文件，但 daemon 仍在运行（60s 空闲超时）。新 Vim 连不上已删的 socket，启动新 daemon，新 daemon 也检测不到旧 daemon。修复：Vim 端只关闭 channel，不删 socket，让 daemon 自己管理生命周期。","original_size":null,"owner":"loyalpartner@163.com","payload":"","pinned":0,"priority":1,"quality_score":null,"rig":"","role_bead":"","role_type":"","sender":"","source_repo":"","source_system":"","spec_id":"","status":"closed","target":"","timeout_ns":0,"title":"Fix: 退出 Vim 后 yacd 进程未清理，重新打开产生重复进程","updated_at":"2026-03-03T15:47:02Z","waiters":"","wisp_type":"","work_type":""}
